{
  "high_level_description": "A vertical editorial fashion portrait photograph of a young female cybernetic android in a wet yellow rain-dress standing under a red transparent umbrella on a rain-soaked neon-lit downtown street at night, shot on 85mm at f/1.4 with shallow depth of field and cinematic neon bokeh.",
  "compositional_deconstruction": {
    "background": "A rain-soaked downtown street at night rendered as large soft out-of-focus bokeh orbs of magenta, cyan, and amber from distant city storefronts stacked behind the figure, glowing signage and window displays blurred into luminous color pools. Wet asphalt extends beneath, mirror-like and reflecting fragmented magenta, cyan, and amber neon pools stretching downward. Cool-neutral white balance overall with local neon color spill — magenta raking from camera-left, cyan rim-light from the right, warm amber pooling on the pavement. Fine cinematic grain throughout, rain falling across the scene.",
    "elements": [
      {
        "type": "obj",
        "desc": "Red transparent vinyl umbrella filling the upper third of the frame overhead, curved dome geometry intact, condensation droplets running down the canopy. Chrome ribs and central shaft catching magenta and cyan reflections along their curves. Held upright above the android."
      },
      {
        "type": "obj",
